{"tid":815911,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"路斯基：即使重傷，雲加依然支持我","createTime":"2018-09-12T11:27:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-12T11:32:53.000Z","uid":16659,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"83fa61b86726612cb2d59ac6d6485278767bd6f7","tid":815911,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T11:27:24.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=YzKTzRaIzE1QaRxyl3aCTsmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=a473b99a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】前阿仙奴球星路斯基接受訪問，透露自己受傷時，雲加依然對他十分支持。<br />\n<br />\n37歲的路斯基（Tomas Rosick&yacute;）說道：「在我和傷病搏鬥時雲加依然非常支持我，即使他也在經歷艱難時刻。我很高興能和他一起共事這麼長時間，他是偉大的榜樣。 」<br />\n<br />\n上周六，路斯基回到酋長球場參加了阿仙奴傳奇隊與皇馬傳奇隊的元老賽，他依然深受球迷的歡迎，對此他便說：「我覺得他們一直都很喜歡我，全因我在阿仙奴處於困難期時依然很忠心，而且我總是會在球場上為球隊出盡全力。所以我認為他們認同這一點，我對此也感到很高興，因為這就是我的感受。」<br />\n<br />\n談到退役後的生活，路斯基顯然對參與足球訓練毫不留戀：「我很想念比賽，當我在電視上看比賽時，我依然想要去踢球。不過，我並不想念訓練的日常安排，一點都不想念。」"},{"pid":"a8f9bc4f8138ee85ed0c87360556fd64a3d6b81a","tid":815911,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T11:28:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://78.media.tumblr.com/24d15b766ce70aab0d3518d27a2a6843/tumblr_p7jkr5fmzc1sva2fko2_r1_500.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F78.media.tumblr.com%2F24d15b766ce70aab0d3518d27a2a6843%2Ftumblr_p7jkr5fmzc1sva2fko2_r1_500.gif&h=00245851&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雲加真的太好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"660b310c7ac464ca7e7048256afe8f070aae00a3","tid":815911,"uid":36497,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T11:29:58.000Z","msg":"雲加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1383d08e90da67d9e675398598465ca029c9f0ae","tid":815911,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T11:32:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://78.media.tumblr.com/24fe5fc05fc1dcd80acc994fa2923686/tumblr_pdd345sv2t1unaw5fo1_1280.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F78.media.tumblr.com%2F24fe5fc05fc1dcd80acc994fa2923686%2Ftumblr_pdd345sv2t1unaw5fo1_1280.jpg&h=a6fde52b&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}